<title>Hatak chi kaniohmi k čt ∆≤IT51</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hatak chi kaniohmi k čt,
 Chis čs pulla hoka
 H čsh anukchieto hokm čt,
 H čsh minti pullashke.

[V2]
 Himak nitak fehna hoka
 Chis čs pulla hok čt
 Pi hohoŐĪyo fehna hocha,
 Pi hal člli hoke.

[V3]
 Chis čs achukma fehna k čt
 PiŐĪ nukhaŐĪklo hoka,
 H čpi chuŐĪk čsh fehna k čno
 Il ema pullashke.

[V4]
 Hatak k čna fehna hocha
 IŐĪki  čba yok
 Anukcheto fehna hokm čt
 Ola mihintashke

[V5]
 Ik kaniohmi hoh kia
 Himak a fehna ka
 ∆≤m  člhpesa pullashke,
 Ish aiahni hokm čt.

[V6]
 Hatak ikhana chia m čt,
 Ola h čsh mintashke;
 Hatak puta,  člla moma,
 Ola h čsh mintashke.

[V7]
 Himak a fehna hok čno,
 An Chis čs fehna ka
 Im antia li pullashke;
 H čsh ahni pullashke.</lyrics>
<aka>The Same</aka>
</song>